{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[G]Down the long road [C]home I [D]go
[G]Through the rain and [C]through the [D]snow
[Em]Miles and miles of [C]open [D]land
[G]Nothing but the [C]road and [D]sand
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[C]Take me [G]home, take me [D]home
[Em]I've been [C]gone too [D]long
[C]Take me [G]home, take me [D]home
[Em]Where my [C]heart be[G]longs
{end_of_chorus}
